YouTube TV

Brief:

YouTube TV is a premium live TV streaming service that offers a diverse selection of content, including live broadcasts from major networks, series, movies, sports events, and kid-friendly channels. With the latest update, YouTube TV has introduced 5.1 audio support for an immersive surround sound experience, initially available on select devices like Google TV, Android TV, and Roku devices. The platform is expanding to include additional devices, enhancing its accessibility across different platforms.
